---
// Testimonials section
---

<section id="testimonials">
  <div class="section-container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">Testimonials</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">What people say</h2>

    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
        <p class="testimonial-quote">I had the privilege of working alongside Raffaele at Accenture Song. He
          consistently demonstrates a genuine willingness to assist, support, and mentor less experienced
          colleagues. Through numerous pair coding sessions, I learned extensively. His patience and eagerness to
          explain concepts have significantly contributed to my professional growth. Raffaele stands out as a
          remarkably positive, supportive, and kind colleague.</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <strong>Claudia Benedetti</strong>
          <span>Product Engineer, Accenture Song</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p class="testimonial-quote">Working with Raffaele is a certainty of success. Creative, competent and
          reliable. Able to transform complex things in simple actions. Raffaele is a detail-oriented manager who
          watches the goal target like a hawk without losing the strategic objective.</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <strong>Claudio Anastasio</strong>
          <span>Colleague &amp; Client, EgoRego</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
        <p class="testimonial-quote">Raffaele has a very positive predisposition to teamwork and he uses a well
          defined perspective, being exceptionally creative at the same time. His innate curiosity allows him to be
          always well-informed and highly knowledgeable about all the innovations in his field.</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <strong>Maria Savarese</strong>
          <span>Communication Expert</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p class="testimonial-quote">Raffaele is very detail oriented. Great quick thinker. His frameworks for
          crisis management on social networks are awesome. A great professional to work with.</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <strong>Simone Favarin</strong>
          <span>Product Designer, UX Consultant</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonials-extra" id="testimonials-extra">
        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">Raffaele è uno sviluppatore e CEO molto attivo, ben organizzato e competente.
            I lavori svolti sotto la sua supervisione sono sempre risultati veloci e ben strutturati.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Valentino Tombesi</strong>
            <span>Frontend Lead, Assist Digital</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">I have had the pleasure of working with Raffaele. I think that he is one of
            the most professional people I know: having a great ability to work hard, he is a very efficient person.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Giorgia Tribuiani</strong>
            <span>Author, Fazi Editore</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">Raffaele was precious in our team introducing some effective web developing
            tools and contributing effortfully to the content creation and publishing.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Diego De Vita</strong>
            <span>Senior Full Stack Developer, CINECA</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">Invidio la visione che Raffaele ha del web. È un "enthusiast" nel senso
            stretto del termine: affronta ogni progetto con una carica invidiabile.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Riccardo Esposito</strong>
            <span>Senior Copywriter</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">Un ottimo professionista, Raffaele, e con una spiccata vocazione per il
            lavoro di squadra. Mi ha colpito per la passione, la disponibilità e la capacità di integrare con
            successo le idee altrui.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Luca Sappino</strong>
            <span>Journalist, Verve Media Company</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">Raffaele è un manager scrupoloso, pieno di idee e di creatività, segue il
            progetto nei minimi dettagli ed è sempre attento a raggiungere gli obiettivi fissati.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Sara Stella</strong>
            <span>Music Marketing Specialist</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">Raffaele è stato il mio superiore durante un'esperienza di stage presso
            EgoRego. Determinato nel suo lavoro, disponibile e attento alle richieste di clienti e dipendenti,
            è un professionista giovane, ma estremamente capace.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Gloria Maria Rossi</strong>
            <span>Teacher</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">Ho conosciuto Raffaele alla LUMSA, quando entrambi eravamo collaboratori di
            cattedra di editoria multimediale. Raffaele è una persona precisa e concreta.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Luisa Bianco</strong>
            <span>Marketing Consultant</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
          <p class="testimonial-quote">Professionale, puntuale, preciso. Persona dinamica seria ed affidabile.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Ginevra Tosoni</strong>
            <span>Entrepreneur</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-toggle reveal">
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" id="testimonials-btn" onclick="window.__toggleTestimonials()">Show more</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
